title: Supreme Court to decide on charges against Brasília police chiefs for January 8 riots
description:
The Supreme Court is debating whether to accept charges against seven high-ranking Brasília police officers for facilitating the January 8 riots in 2023, when thousands of far-right radicals stormed and ransacked the buildings of the three branches of government in Brazil’s capital.
